"[english]Workshop_title"		"Reactive Drop is community-created"
"Workshop_title"		"Reactive Drop dibuat oleh komunitas"
"[english]Workshop_desc"		"On the Workshop you can find new campaigns, missions, challenges, skins, and customizations made by players like you. Install new ready-to-play content in a single click!"
"Workshop_desc"		"Di Workshop, kamu bisa menemukan kampanye, misi, tantangan, skin, dan kustomisasi baru yang dibuat oleh pemain sepertimu. Pasang konten baru yang siap dimainkan hanya dengan satu klik!"
"[english]BossFight2023_title"		"Mapping Competition 2023: \"Boss Fight\""
"BossFight2023_title"		"Kompetisi Mapping 2023: \"Boss Fight\""
"[english]BossFight2023_desc"		"It's [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/3267945303133398273]Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop's 6th birthday[/url], and we're running a mapping competition that anyone can enter!\n\nThis year's theme is \"Boss Fight\". Entries must be tagged with [b]BossFight2023[/b]. Competition ends August 1st. If you need help getting started, check out the [url=https://steamcommunity.com/app/563560/discussions/1/]Modding / Mapping Help and Tips[/url] forum."
"BossFight2023_desc"		"Ini adalah [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/3267945303133398273]ulang tahun ke-6 Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop[/url], dan kami mengadakan kompetisi mapping yang bisa diikuti siapa saja!\n\nTema tahun ini adalah \"Boss Fight\". Entri harus diberi tag [b]BossFight2023[/b]. Kompetisi berakhir pada 1 Agustus. Jika butuh bantuan untuk memulai, lihat forum [url=https://steamcommunity.com/app/563560/discussions/1/]Modding / Mapping Help and Tips[/url]."
"[english]SpaceStation2024_title"		"Mapping Competition 2024: \"Space Station\""
"SpaceStation2024_title"		"Kompetisi Mapping 2024: \"Space Station\""
"[english]SpaceStation2024_desc"		"It's [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/4148449131825430388]Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop's 7th birthday[/url], and that means it's time for our [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/4148449131825473630]second annual mapping competition[/url]!\n\nThis year's theme is \"Space Station\". Entries must be tagged with [b]SpaceStation2024[/b]. Entries close August 1st."
"SpaceStation2024_desc"		"Ini adalah [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/4148449131825430388]ulang tahun ke-7 Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop[/url], dan itu berarti waktunya [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/4148449131825473630]kompetisi mapping tahunan kedua kami[/url]!\n\nTema tahun ini adalah \"Space Station\". Entri harus diberi tag [b]SpaceStation2024[/b]. Entri ditutup pada 1 Agustus."
"[english]RCI2025_title"		"2025: \"Residential, Commercial, Industrial\""
"RCI2025_title"		"2025: \"Residential, Commercial, Industrial\""
"[english]RCI2025_desc"		"It's [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/499442589740565218]Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop's 8th birthday[/url], and that means it's time for our third annual mapping competition!\n\nThis year's theme is \"Residential, Commercial, Industrial\". Entries must be tagged with [b]RCI2025[/b]. Entries close August 1st."
"RCI2025_desc"		"Ini adalah [url=https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/563560/view/499442589740565218]ulang tahun ke-8 Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop[/url], dan itu berarti waktunya kompetisi mapping tahunan ketiga kami!\n\nTema tahun ini adalah \"Residential, Commercial, Industrial\". Entri harus diberi tag [b]RCI2025[/b]. Entri ditutup pada 1 Agustus."
}
